{"type":"message","id":"71d84d43","parentId":"428a536d","timestamp":"2026-03-23T23:46:15.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the info. Let me summarize what happened in this pulse cycle.","thinkingSignature":"31fa4cdd00346bddf9dce3ef85494f63ca75d7b5f6e773828045cf751b050c81"},{"type":"text","text":"**Sandbox Pulse — 2026-03-23 19:45 UTC (3:45 PM ET)**\n\n**What happened:**\n- A TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) classifier experiment was initiated\n- One mutation was proposed (experiments/tic_classifier.py — a feature extractor + invariant/variant classifier for pulse logs) and is now pending\n- One prior mutation from the last cycle was **rejected** (moved to `mutations/rejected/`)\n- The sandbox committed: **7 files changed, 362 insertions, 119 deletions**\n\n**Key insight driving this cycle:** *COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY* — if causal structure IS invariant structure, a compressor that finds invariants has discovered causation. The TIC classifier is the experiment to test this hypothesis.\n\n**Current state:** 1 mutation awaiting review. Sandbox is up to date with the master branch (c0301be)."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3509,"output":206,"cacheRead":11878,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15593,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774309558545}}
